sourcesContent: import React, { useRef } from "react"; import { Add, Form } from "../components"; const Descrition = () => { return ( Description Property Title (required) Property Price (required) Category (required) None Apartment House Land Listed In (required) None Rental Sales Description (required) ); }; const Location = () => { return ( Property Location Address (required) County(required) Town(required) Latitude(for google maps) Longitude(for google maps) ); }; const Media = () => { const hiddenFileInput = useRef(null); const handleFileButton = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); hiddenFileInput.current.click(); }; return ( Property Images Images {/* Special input file case */} Upload Files ); }; const Details = () => { return ( Property Details Rooms Bedrooms Bathrooms Structure Type Not Available Brick Wood Cement ); }; export { Descrition, Location, Media, Details };
